{"tid":615023,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[4月新番已經出左]宇宙戰艦提拉米斯 宇宙戦艦ティラミス 集中討論","createTime":"2018-04-03T04:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T04:53:57.000Z","uid":3020,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6e80d4486448427f737573b972bdd692632961c2","tid":615023,"uid":3020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T04:53:57.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/d9Kjdjs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fd9Kjdjs.png&h=3213e462&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qeyTVJ2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FqeyTVJ2.png&h=cafce2bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡介<br />\n以戰艦中駕駛著專用機「狄蘭達爾」的王牌駕駛員「昴・一之瀨」為中心所展開的搞笑科幻故事。在動畫中將由 石川界人擔綱主演配音，參與演出的還有 櫻井孝宏、諏訪部順一、江口拓也、大塚明夫（擔任旁白）等人。<br />\n<br />\nSTAFF<br />\n原作：伊藤亰、宮川サトシ<br />\n監督：博史池畠<br />\n系列構成：佐藤裕<br />\n角色造型：橫山愛<br />\n動畫製作：GONZO<br />\n<br />\nCAST<br />\n一之瀨昴：石川界人<br />\n一之瀨五十鈴：櫻井孝宏<br />\n沃爾加&middot;哈瑪：諏訪部順一<br />\n昴B：江口拓也<br />\n旁白：大塚明夫<br />\nPV<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y727LMEvH6c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY727LMEvH6c&d=DF0wBaBGUr8MGd9%2B%2FFq5KaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7ff22b94\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y727LMEvH6c</a><br />\n公式<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tiramisu-anime.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiramisu-anime.com%2F&d=DF0wBaBGUr8MGd9%2B%2FFq5KaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=8baece17\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tiramisu-anime.com/</a><br />\n線上<br />\n<a href=\"http://myself-bbs.com/thread-43590-1-1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmyself-bbs.com%2Fthread-43590-1-1.html&d=DF0wBaBGUr8MGd9%2B%2FFq5KaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=609f3038\" target=\"_blank\">http://myself-bbs.com/thread-43590-1-1.html</a></div>"}]}